@startuml
' A compiled LocalMachine showing all three EdgeKinds: Internal (ordinary comm),
' Call (push a return frame), Return (pop). This is the orchestrator O of a
' call-bearing protocol. Palette: internal=slate, call/push=violet, return/pop=fuchsia,
' terminal=green.
skinparam backgroundColor transparent
skinparam defaultFontName Inter
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #e2e8f0
  BorderColor #334155
  FontColor #0f172a
}

[*] --> s0
s0 : initial
s0 -[#475569]-> s1 : Send(Sub, subcall) / Internal
s1 -[#7c3aed,bold]-> box : "call:recursive_cf" / **Call{return_state = s2}**  (PUSH)
box : callee box entry\n(compiled once · reused)
box -[#475569]-> box2 : … callee body (Internal) …
box2 -[#c026d3,bold]-> s2 : End / **Return**  (POP → return_state)
s2 -[#475569]-> s3 : Recv(Sub, subresult) / Internal
s3 --> [*]
s3 : terminal

note right of box
  recursive callee back-edges to its own
  box entry: finite syntax, unbounded
  nesting bounded by MAX_STACK_DEPTH
end note
@enduml
